(24, 1, '2016-01-30 23:33:47', '2016-01-30 23:33:47', '<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-22" src="http://beta.freeformportland.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/freeform-portland-trout-mask.png" alt="Freeform Portland Trout Mask" width="700" height="698" />\r\n<h1>LowPower FM</h1>\r\nFreeform, or freeform radio, is a radio station programming format in which the DJ is given total control over what music to play, regardless of music genre or commercial interests.\r\n<h1>Community Driven</h1>\r\nMusic &amp; freeform radio have the power to bring together communities and create human connection that is becoming increasingly valuable in our digital age.', 'Homepage', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-30 23:33:47', '2016-01-30 23:33:47', '', 5, 'http://beta.freeformportland.org/2016/01/30/5-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
