(74, 2, '2016-02-17 05:31:37', '2016-02-17 05:31:37', '<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-22" src="http://beta.freeformportland.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/freeform-portland-trout-mask.png" alt="Freeform Portland Trout Mask" width="700" height="698" />\r\n<h1>Radio for the People, by the People</h1>\r\nFreeform Portland (KFFP 90.3 FM) is a nonprofit, independent community radio station whose purpose is to foster independent, local, experimental, and underground music, alongside arts and public affairs programming that reflect our community. Freeform Portland is radio for the people, by the people.\r\n\r\nMusic and freeform radio have the power to bring together communities and create human connection. Despite having a metro area of over two million people, Portland has very few non-commercial, independent stations on the air. Freeform Portland provides a venue for more local voices and cultural perspectives from our music and arts communities to be heard.', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-17 05:31:37', '2016-02-17 05:31:37', '', 5, 'http://beta.freeformportland.org/blog/5-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(75, 3, '2016-02-17 05:57:16', '2016-02-17 05:57:16', 'Freeform Portland is a 501(3)c nonprofit organization benefiting our community through providing a number of public resources:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>X</li>\r\n	<li>Y</li>\r\n	<li>Z</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur station is on the air thanks to volunteer and financial support from our friends and neighbors and we are grateful for any and all contributions.\r\n\r\nDonations to Freeform Portland can be tax-deductible! Secure and convenient one-time or recurring donations can be made via PayPal:\r\n\r\n[PayPal button]\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We also happily accept checks. Please make out checks to Freeform Portland and mail to:\r\nFreeform Portland\r\n801 N. Killingsworth St.\r\nPortland OR 97217.</p>\r\nWe also gratefully accept in-kind donations of records, CDs and headphones in good working condition, plus office supplies, snacks, and more — please email TKTK@freeformportland.org to discuss your donation with a member of our volunteer staff. You can also keep an eye out for the donation jar at most KFFP events.\r\n\r\nThanks so much!', 'Donate', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-17 05:57:16', '2016-02-17 05:57:16', '', 32, 'http://beta.freeformportland.org/blog/32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
