(165, 1, '2016-03-21 03:15:12', '2016-03-21 03:15:12', 'Each week you get either a live broadcast from Beech Street Parlor, or from The Soup Caves... deep inside Another Planet.\r\n<div>Zaph Mann''s IMOJP (In Memory Of John Peel) Show, adheres to the style and values of the late great DJ John Peel: Breaking edgy new music from outside the mainstream in a mesmerising mix of genres. Often #1 in the worldwide freeform charts, selected the best show *anywhere* to here new music by the UK''s Louder Than War - you won''t like it all, but you''ll hear something special, ahead of the crowd.</div>', 'Live from Beech St Parlor / Zaph Mann''s IMOJP Show (Alternating)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'live-remote-zaph', '', '', '2016-10-10 06:37:34', '2016-10-10 06:37:34', '', 0, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/?post_type=show&#038;p=165', 0, 'show', '', 0),
