(169, 110, '2016-03-21 03:19:16', '2016-03-21 03:19:16', '<div>\r\n\r\nWeekend Family Music Hour is children led by DJs Kawaii &amp; Devil Child who are 8 &amp; 10 yrs old. They are supervised by Mom (Karen) &amp; we play eclectic music which ranges from ethnic, Miami bass, soul, funk, rock, psych, hip hop, reggae, jazz &amp; folk. Birthday shout outs with Miami Bass song by Luke Skywalker, “It’s Your Birthday.” Child led discussions on politics, magic and childhood subjects.\r\n\r\nWe bring our Moog in for ambience on holidays or special occasions.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-485" src="http://www.freeformportland.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/unnamed.jpg" alt="image" width="724" height="724" />', 'Weekend Family Music Hour', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'weekend-family-music-hour', '', '', '2017-03-27 21:38:23', '2017-03-28 04:38:23', '', 0, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/?post_type=show&#038;p=169', 0, 'show', '', 0),
