(930, 3, '2016-10-09 21:53:43', '2016-10-09 21:53:43', 'The Funk Pharmacy gives listeners the best soul and funk music that they have ever heard, along with all of the cuts that they have never heard. Dr. Soul is cocked, locked, and ready to rock to fill your prescription when he jumps on the 1''s and 2''s. Jammin'', rammin'', and always slamming the hits through your speakers, he delivers what you need tight and right every time. Come get down to the greatest jams on the only station you need on your FM dial, 90.3 KFFP. Dig it, P-Town!', 'The Funk Pharmacy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-funk-pharmacy', '', '', '2017-03-31 20:19:20', '2017-04-01 03:19:20', '', 0, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/?post_type=show&#038;p=930', 0, 'show', '', 0),
(179, 38, '2016-03-21 03:34:00', '2016-03-21 03:34:00', 'The goal of this program will be to take the listeners on an adventure across musical styles and time. This wide-ranging mix will hop across genres as diverse as cosmic American, psychedelic, all varieties of jazz, American primitive, soul, and garage. However, hopping to these genres will not be the extent of the journey as the goal of the program will be to use any means necessary (e.g., a pogo stick, time-traveling Delorean, amphibious vehicle, etc.) to scour the musical universe to bring back entertaining and interesting sounds to the audience.', 'Universal Sound', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'universal-sound-w-dj-eroc', '', '', '2017-03-31 20:18:56', '2017-04-01 03:18:56', '', 0, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/?post_type=show&#038;p=179', 0, 'show', '', 0),
