(219, 11, '2016-03-21 04:04:40', '2016-03-21 04:04:40', 'A DIY oriented radio show focusing on underground music, both local and international, from the past and present that mocks the question: \\"What sub-genre would you call this?\\" This show connects different underground scenes that exist separately from each other based on genre, focusing on punk, metal, noise, outsider, and many sub genres in between. New demos of honest, untested bands from around the world are the things that would keep this show going. Each show begins with the local scene report that exposes the bands that are playing frequently around town or just came out with a new demo or album. Root for the underdogs! This show would give me a chance to display these lesser known bands within a cohesive but eclectic playlist of other more established like-minded artists in hopes to tie various DIY scenes in Portland for a more tight knit community.', 'What Sub Genre', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-sub-genre-w-dj-dishpit', '', '', '2016-10-09 23:31:15', '2016-10-09 23:31:15', '', 0, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/?post_type=show&#038;p=219', 0, 'show', '', 0),
