(387, 3, '2016-03-28 18:30:59', '2016-03-28 18:30:59', 'Sultry, strange, well worn and new teritory. A weekly two hour show featuring an eclectic mix of old and new tracks from soul, hip hop, and r&amp;b to instrumental and indie. A NE Portland native, I started compiling tracks as a kid with a tape cassette. My lifelong project of creating soundtracks to the lives near and dear to me would be enhanced if I could share with the Portland community.', 'The Waters', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '232-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-03-28 18:30:59', '2016-03-28 18:30:59', '', 232, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/232-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
