(248, 3, '2016-03-23 14:12:41', '2016-03-23 14:12:41', '<h1 style="text-align: center;">Donate</h1>\r\nFreeform Portland is a nonprofit organization, pending 501(3)c status, benefiting our community through providing a number of public resources:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Broadcasting Musicology classes</li>\r\n	<li>Music library</li>\r\n	<li>Promoting local music and arts events</li>\r\n	<li>More!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur station runs on volunteer and financial support from our friends and neighbors and we are grateful for any and all contributions.\r\n\r\nYour donation to Freeform Portland can be tax-deductible!\r\n\r\n<form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top"><input name="cmd" type="hidden" value="_s-xclick" /><input name="hosted_button_id" type="hidden" value="EXDPWNQFGWYEL" /><input alt="Donate to KFFP" name="submit" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donate_LG.gif" type="image" /></form>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Feel free to send a check, if  you''d like. Please make checks out to Freeform Portland and mail to:\r\nFreeform Portland\r\n801 N. Killingsworth St.\r\nPortland OR 97217</p>\r\nFreeform Portland will gratefully accept your donation of records, CDs and headphones in good working condition, plus office supplies, snacks, and more — please email donate@freeformportland.org to get in touch with a donations volunteer. You can also keep an eye out for the donation jar at most KFFP events.\r\n\r\nThanks so much!', 'Donate', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-23 14:12:41', '2016-03-23 14:12:41', '', 32, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
