(291, 1, '2016-03-25 03:26:27', '2016-03-25 03:26:27', 'Music Shelved Dreams is a music program devoted to DJ mixes of dance music with improbably wide parameters: romantic, dark, uplifting, rhythmic, abstract, melodramatic, minimal, international, crude, homemade, underground. Discussion shies away from genre descriptors, favoring  more integrated signifiers such as aesthetic, cultural and geographic context, artistic and creative process. Concise interviews and guest appearances whenever possible to illuminate the undergrounds of Portland and beyond. Hour 1 - formatted for more abstract compositions, slower BPM''s, mood setting, mixed, not necessarily beatmatched Hour 2 - hour long mix, beatmatched and continuous (w/ongoing talkover announcements, PSA''s and commentary)', 'Shelved Dreams', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '240-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-03-25 03:26:27', '2016-03-25 03:26:27', '', 240, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/240-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
