(333, 41, '2016-03-25 04:40:35', '2016-03-25 04:40:35', 'Curb Service first and foremost is a music show, though hopefully just the right amount of silliness will grace each show. It is carefully curated to showcase a wide variety of music and is only bound by Eddie''s ability to sift through the endless stacks. You can expect to hear plenty of music you don''t know, but also plenty of music you do know. The goal is not to shock you into realizing you actually know nothing about the gross scope of micro music genres that exist and you are an alien on your own planet, but rather to mix together great music regardless of genre, popularity or the decade of its recording. If Eddie likes it and it is deemed appropriate by the FCC then Eddie will play it...To put it shortly, Curb Service wants to provide its listeners with the stylish and luxurious listening experience they deserve. Sit back, relax and enjoy...', 'Curb Service', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '216-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-03-25 04:40:35', '2016-03-25 04:40:35', '', 216, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/216-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
