(339, 23, '2016-03-25 04:51:03', '2016-03-25 04:51:03', 'Studio Visit is a curated forum for PDX-area artists, art professionals, art lovers, and creatives of all kinds. DJ Abi will host the show, and each week a new guest will accompany her for an exploration of their own personal music tastes, creative process, and random daydreams. The show will be 1/3rd talk and 2/3rds music, but the music will be eclectic by definition because the guests will determine the playlist. DJ Abi will engage guests in casual conversation about how music affects their artistic practice, what music obsessions they have and why, memories of the local music scene, and what makes them tick creatively in general. These exchanges will be interspersed with music sets created by the guest in advance with DJ Abi''s advice.', 'Studio Visit', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '196-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-03-25 04:51:03', '2016-03-25 04:51:03', '', 196, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/196-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
