(341, 41, '2016-03-25 04:51:28', '2016-03-25 04:51:28', 'I want to play music and interview people who are involved in the arts and fringe areas of the counterculture.\\n\\nI''d also like to discuss completely crazy conspiracy theories. Mostly fabricated for the show, and generally centered around music. sort of things like \\"\\"I read online...\\"\\" or I saw this blog, its been deleted but it talked about...\\"\\" examples:\\n\\n-Jimi Hendrix assassination plot by British MI5 and Eric Clapton\\n\\n-Charles Manson was a CIA operative sent to give the Beach Boys inside info on The Beatles new records (in an attempt to further american culture internationally and block brits from influencing the young american) when that went south, Manson was reassigned to destroy the hippie movement all together.\\n\\n-The B52''s entire project was a cover for a murder-for-hire group.\\n\\nThis portion of the show would be really improved by being able to take calls from listeners...\\', 'Jam the Controls', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '197-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-03-25 04:51:28', '2016-03-25 04:51:28', '', 197, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/197-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
