(873, 3, '2016-10-06 02:23:46', '2016-10-06 02:23:46', '<a href="/drive"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-580" src="/images/meter/10.jpg" alt="Freeform Portland Vinyl DJs" width="700" height="999" /></a>\r\n<h1>October 1 – 7 Donor Drive</h1>\r\nFreeform Portland is kicking off a <a href="http://www.freeformportland.org/drive/">donor drive</a> on October 1st, and we’re offering one-of-a-kind gifts for donations made during the week of October 1 – 7! Help us stay on air, improve our broadcast signal, and continue to offer unique opportunities and services to the Portland community. <a href="http://www.freeformportland.org/drive/">Click here</a> to donate and learn more about the October Donor Drive.\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: 16px;">Freeform Portland KFFP-LP 90.3 FM is run by a dedicated group of music enthusiasts and DJs from Portland, Oregon. We''re local volunteers who want to reclaim some portion of our airwaves from corporate control.</span>\r\n\r\nWe offer:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Public broadcasting classes and music education opportunities</li>\r\n	<li>DJs with unique cultural perspectives and fresh voices from the local community</li>\r\n	<li>Exposure to local and touring musicians</li>\r\n	<li>Experimental music and arts programming, under-represented in Portland</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLet''s uphold community radio and freeform programming that truly reflects and celebrates our local communities.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-06 02:23:46', '2016-10-06 02:23:46', '', 5, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/5-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
