ating</h1>\r\nIf you <a href="http://www.freeformportland.org/donate/" target="_blank">donate</a> during the October Donor Drive, we''ll send you an email to select one of the special edition gifts listed below to thank you for your donation and support!\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-797 alignleft" src="http://www.freeformportland.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/MockupTshirt-300x280.jpg" alt="MockupTshirt" width="300" height="280" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Limited edition Freeform Portland t-shirt for $20+, or $15+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition Freeform Portland tote bag for $20+, or $15+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Official Freeform Portland hoodie for $40+, or $15 per month</li>\r\n	<li>Your favorite Freeform Portland DJ will DJ your party for a $100+ donation</li>\r\n	<li>Special thank you mix by a Freeform Portland DJ (we''ll email you choices when you donate) for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>A drawing by The Queen of Siam (The Upstairs Room) for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition Deep Lez Power Hour frosted etched glass for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition handmade and hand-screenprinted The Guitar and Other Machines record bag for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Rat tin prepared for you by DJ Mrrranda of Spider in the Ear for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition shirt from Teen &amp; Quoz of Terminal Beach for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Piece of artwork by DJ Zach of Zach''s Radio Show for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Surprise handmade package from Eeronomicon for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Artwork by DJ RK Heist from Sounds Obscure for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Copy of a ransom letter, photos of Rusty Nail in captivity, and special thank you mix by Dusty Dale for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition Alleys of Your Mind poster for a $50+ donation</li>\r\n	<li>Tour of Freeform Portland with our radio engineer for a $50+ donation</li>\r\n	<li>Special thank you batch of CDs from Bloodshot Records in Chicago brought to you by DJ HRPunknStuf for $30+, or $15+ per month</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.freeformportland.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/weekend-family-music-hour-ad.png" target="_blank">Kid sing along of Buffy Vampire the Slayer "Once More, With Feeling" musical verbatim</a> from Weekend Family Music Hour for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>DJ Zaph Mann''s grab bag of rare CDs for $40+, or $20+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Special merch pack from NONNA of Well Worn and New Territory for a $50+ donation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<form style="margin-bottom: 1em;" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top"><input name="cmd" type="hidden" value="_s-xclick" /><input name="hosted_button_id" type="hidden" value="EXDPWNQFGWYEL" /><input alt="Donate to KFFP" name="submit" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donate_LG.gif" type="image" /></form>', 'Donor Drive', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '772-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-30 03:35:12', '2016-09-30 03:35:12', '', 772, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/772-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
