(840, 3, '2016-09-30 16:54:19', '2016-09-30 16:54:19', '<h1>October 1 - 7 Donor Drive\r\nCelebrating Our First Year</h1>\r\n<form style="margin-bottom: 1em;" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top"><input name="cmd" type="hidden" value="_s-xclick" /><input name="hosted_button_id" type="hidden" value="EXDPWNQFGWYEL" /><input alt="Donate to KFFP" name="submit" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donate_LG.gif" type="image" /></form><img class="size-medium wp-image-817 alignright" src="http://www.freeformportland.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/The-Hunger-Is-Real-292x300.png" alt="Art for KFFP by Melissa Chalhoub" width="292" height="300" />Over the past year Freeform Portland grew from its crowd-funded beginnings in Portland, Oregon to become the creative and educational community of DJs and music lovers that it is today. Over 100 local volunteers now contribute to our unique, diverse programming 24/7, streaming online worldwide at freeformportland.org, and broadcasting locally at 90.3 FM from the Baker Building in North Portland.\r\n\r\nTo celebrate our first year we''re kicking off a donor drive on October 1st, and we''re offering one-of-a-kind gifts for donations made during the week of October 1 - 7! See below for a list of our donor drive premiums.\r\n<h1>Help Us Stay Up and Running!</h1>\r\nAfter raising $11,000 for our initial launch, we now ask listeners and our community to help us raise $15,000 to keep Freeform Portland up and running. By clicking the Donate button at the top of the page you''ll personally help us stay on air, improve our broadcast signal, and continue to offer unique opportunities and services to the Portland community. We''re a 501(3)(c) nonprofit organization, and so your donation is tax deductible.\r\n\r\nThank you for listening, participating, and supporting the availability of community freeform radio. Be sure to check out our special Donor Drive offerings, below!\r\n<h1>Premiums for Donating</h1>\r\nIf you donate during the October Donor Drive, we''ll send you an email to select one of the special edition gifts listed below to thank you for your donation and support!\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-797 alignleft" src="http://www.freeformportland.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/MockupTshirt-300x280.jpg" alt="MockupTshirt" width="300" height="280" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Limited edition Freeform Portland t-shirt for $20+, or $15+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition Freeform Portland tote bag for $20+, or $15+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Official Freeform Portland hoodie for $40+, or $15 per month</li>\r\n	<li>Your favorite Freeform Portland DJ will DJ your party for a $100+ donation</li>\r\n	<li>Special thank you mix by a Freeform Portland DJ (we''ll email you choices when you donate) for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>A drawing by The Queen of Siam (The Upstairs Room) for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition Deep Lez Power Hour frosted etched glass for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition handmade and hand-screenprinted The Guitar and Other Machines record bag for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Rat tin prepared for you by DJ Mrrranda of Spider in the Ear for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition shirt from Teen &amp; Quoz of Terminal Beach for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Piece of artwork by DJ Zach of Zach''s Radio Show for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Surprise handmade package from DJs Gilliflower &amp; Eeronomicon for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Artwork by DJ RK Heist from Sounds Obscure for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Copy of a ransom letter, photos of Rusty Nail in captivity, and special thank you mix by Dusty Dale for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition Alleys of Your Mind poster for a $50+ donation</li>\r\n	<li>Tour of Freeform Portland with our radio engineer for a $50+ donation</li>\r\n	<li>Special thank you batch of CDs from Bloodshot Records in Chicago brought to you by DJ HRPunknStuf for $30+, or $15+ per month</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.freeformportland.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/weekend-family-music-hour-ad.png" target="_blank">Kid sing along of Buffy Vampire the Slayer "Once More, With Feeling" musical verbatim</a> from Weekend Family Music Hour for $25+, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>DJ Zaph Mann''s grab bag of rare CDs for $40+, or $20+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Special merch pack from NONNA of Well Worn and New Territory for a $50+ donation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<form style="margin-bottom: 1em;" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top"><input name="cmd" type="hidden" value="_s-xclick" /><input name="hosted_button_id" type="hidden" value="EXDPWNQFGWYEL" /><input alt="Donate to KFFP" name="submit" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donate_LG.gif" type="image" /></form>', 'Donor Drive', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '772-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-30 16:54:19', '2016-09-30 16:54:19', '', 772, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/772-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
