tion, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition handmade and hand-screenprinted The Guitar and Other Machines record bag for $25+ donation, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Rat tin prepared for you by DJ Mrrranda of Spider in the Ear for $25+ donation, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Limited edition shirt from Teen &amp; Quoz of Terminal Beach for $25+ donation, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Piece of artwork by DJ Zach of Zach''s Radio Show for $25+ donation, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Surprise handmade package from DJs Gilliflower &amp; Eeronomicon for $25+ donation, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Artwork by DJ RK Heist from Sounds Obscure for $25+ donation, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Copy of a ransom letter, photos of Rusty Nail in captivity, and special thank you mix by Dusty Dale for $25+ donation, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Tour of Freeform Portland with our radio engineer for a $50+ donation</li>\r\n	<li>Special thank you batch of CDs from Bloodshot Records in Chicago brought to you by DJ HRPunknStuf for $30+ donation, or $15+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>DJ Zaph Mann''s grab bag of rare CDs for $40+ donation, or $20+ per month</li>\r\n	<li>Special merch pack from NONNA of Well Worn and New Territory for a $50+ donation</li>\r\n	<li>Special thank you mixtape + handmade art by DJs Olive and Dan from File Under Various for $25+ donation, or $10+ per month</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<form style="margin-bottom: 1em;" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top"><input name="cmd" type="hidden" value="_s-xclick" /><input name="hosted_button_id" type="hidden" value="EXDPWNQFGWYEL" /><input alt="Donate to KFFP" name="submit" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donate_LG.gif" type="image" /></form>', 'Donor Drive', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '772-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-30 19:38:57', '2016-09-30 19:38:57', '', 772, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/772-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
