(1304, 128, '2017-03-31 20:19:46', '2017-04-01 03:19:46', 'Terminal Beach explores the multi-faceted and ever-evolving field of electronic music, with an emphasis on techno, house, bass, funk, electro, industrial, experimental and ambient styles. And sometimes we play Three 6 Mafia instrumentals.\r\nWe also seek to host a variety of local artists and DJs for guest performances, and to shine a light on local and international record labels and music scenes/collectives.', 'Terminal Beach', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '174-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-03-31 20:19:46', '2017-04-01 03:19:46', '', 174, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/174-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
