(965, 128, '2016-10-10 05:37:27', '2016-10-10 05:37:27', 'Mudclub, Berghain, Batcave, Clit Club, The Spectrum, and now Club Mate. Sexy music for the glittering, revolutionary, downtown crowd. Current and classic cuts across genre.\r\n\r\nMUSIC IS OUR WEAPON. MUSIC IS THEE COMMON DENOMINATOR. OUR RELIGION IS BEAUTY. WE WIELD ONLY THE SWORD OF FLAWLESSNESS. OUR ANGER IS OUTWEIGHED ONLY BY OUR DESIRE FOR GORGEOUSNESS. WE''VE COME TO DESTROY THE MAN, RECLAIM THE FEMININE IDENTITY, AND ANCHOR THE WHITE LIGHT FOR ALL BEINGS. WE CONSCIOUSLY ERADICATE THE FEAR WE''VE BEEN PROGRAMMED TO HAVE IN OUR HEARTS, AND THAT''S WHY WE''RE SO MUTHAFUCKIN BAD.\r\n\r\nThis is our soundtrack.\r\n\r\nSludge. Vogue. House. Deathrock. Doom. Digital Hardcore. Italo Disco. Industrial. New Age. New Romantic. Punk. Avant Garde. Techno. Rave. Ambient. Yé-yé Grrrl. Hip Hop. Trip Hop. Dub. Voodoo. Acid. Ecstasy. Animals. High Heels. Long Nails. Shaved Headed Girls and Longhaired Boys. Whatever.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Club-Mate', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'club-mate', '', '', '2017-03-27 21:11:51', '2017-03-28 04:11:51', '', 0, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/?post_type=show&#038;p=965', 0, 'show', '', 0),
