(1331, 128, '2017-03-31 21:59:17', '2017-04-01 04:59:17', '<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-627 aligncenter" src="http://www.freeformportland.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/The-Geeks-Were-Right-BSG_Blue-v2.png" alt="The Geeks Were Right BSG_Blue-v2" width="480" height="480" />\n<p style="text-align: center;">The Geeks Were Right //<span style="font-size: small;"> </span>I am DJ D //<span style="font-size: small;"><b> </b></span>For Two Hours // Everything Electronic //<b> </b>Sundays, Midnight - 2AM</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">The Geeks Were Right is devoted to spinning electronic music spanning from the earliest electronic music to now. Hear tracks from the underground, the obscure and experimental; to the latest, most popular tracks being played today. Tune in to hear electronic music from your neighbors down the street to artists from all across the world.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">The Geeks Were Right will always cover the ever growing range of electronic music from Glitch, IDM, Coldwave, Electropop, Disco, Krautrock, Folktronica, Spacerock, Dub, Chillwave, House and so much more.</p>\n\n<div style="text-align: center;">Mixcloud: <a href="http://mixcloud.com/TheGeeksWereRight" target="_blank" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://mixcloud.com/TheGeeksWereRight&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1480307040151000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHrm3DMZs0wWITlwy8h7bMXdbp1vw">mixcloud.com/TheGeeksWereRight</a></div>\n<div style="text-align: center;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: center;">Twitter: <a href="http://twitter.com/tgwr_djd" target="_blank" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://twitter.com/tgwr_djd&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1480307040151000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHn1tbKcgtzXdldmXben1h_L8H1Xg">twitter.com/tgwr_djd</a></div>\n<div style="text-align: center;"></div>\n<div>\n<div style="text-align: center;">Instagram: <a href="http://instagram.com/thegeekswererightdjd" target="_blank" data-saferedirecturl="https://w