(1250, 128, '2017-03-27 19:32:12', '2017-03-28 02:32:12', 'Providing perspective and catharsis from a juvenile delinquent all grown up and out of the foster care system. Trans riot-grrrl, musician, and all around goofball PTSD-J SkarrKrow plays tunes and occasionally performs spoken word reaching out to those of us in the world left behind and broken in a system that most of us never asked to be a part of as well as those of us who continue to struggle, and we who have survived our own personal hells. Orphan Anthems range from furious &amp; confrontational, melancholy &amp; weeping, sensual &amp; celebratory, and non-sequiturs galore. Be prepared for a presence unabashed, unforgiving, and unrelenting.', 'Orphan Anthems', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'orphan-anthems', '', '', '2017-03-31 20:56:24', '2017-04-01 03:56:24', '', 0, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/?post_type=show&#038;p=1250', 0, 'show', '', 0),
