(1321, 128, '2017-03-31 20:56:25', '2017-04-01 03:56:25', 'Providing perspective and catharsis from a juvenile delinquent all grown up and out of the foster care system. Trans riot-grrrl, musician, and all around goofball PTSD-J SkarrKrow plays tunes and occasionally performs spoken word reaching out to those of us in the world left behind and broken in a system that most of us never asked to be a part of as well as those of us who continue to struggle, and we who have survived our own personal hells. Orphan Anthems range from furious &amp; confrontational, melancholy &amp; weeping, sensual &amp; celebratory, and non-sequiturs galore. Be prepared for a presence unabashed, unforgiving, and unrelenting.', 'Orphan Anthems', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1250-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-03-31 20:56:25', '2017-04-01 03:56:25', '', 1250, 'http://www.freeformportland.org/blog/1250-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
